createLot(uint256,uint256[],uint256,uint.details: Creates a new Lot to add to the sale. There are NO guarantees about the uniqueness of the non-fungible token supply. Lot item price must be at least 0.00001 of the base denomination.

params.fungibleAmount: Initial fungible token amount to bundle with each NFT.
params.lotId: Id of the Lot to create.
params.nonFungibleSupply: Initial non-fungible token supply of the Lot.
params.price: Initial Lot item sale price, in payout currency tokens

getPrice(address,uint256,uint256,address.details: Retrieves user purchase price information for the given quantity of Lot items.

params.lotId: Lot id of the items from which the purchase price information will be retrieved.
params.quantity: Quantity of Lot items from which the purchase price information will be retrieved.
params.recipient: The user for whom the price information is being retrieved for.

returns.minConversionRate: Minimum conversion rate from purchase tokens to payout tokens.
returns.totalDiscounts: Total discounts to apply to the total price, in purchase currency tokens.
returns.totalPrice: Total price (excluding any discounts), in purchase currency tokens.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

peekLotAvailableNonFungibleSupply(uint25.details: Returns the given number of next available non-fungible tokens for the specified Lot.If the given number is more than the next available non-fungible tokens, then the remaining available is returned.

params.count: Number of next available non-fungible tokens to peek.
params.lotId: Id of the Lot whose non-fungible supply to peek into.

returns._0: The given number of next available non-fungible tokens for the specified Lot, otherwise the remaining available non-fungible tokens.

purchaseFor(address,uint256,uint256,addr.details: Purchases a quantity of Lot items for the given Lot id.

params.extData: Additional string encoded custom data to pass through to the event.
params.lotId: Lot id of the items to purchase.
params.maxTokenAmount: Maximum amount of purchase tokens to spend for the purchase.
params.minConversionRate: Minimum conversion rate, from purchase tokens to payout tokens, to allow for the purchase to succeed.
params.quantity: Quantity of Lot items to purchase.
params.recipient: Destination account to receive the purchased Lot items.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setFungibleTokenId(uint256).details: Sets the inventory token id of the fungible tokens bundled in a Lot item.

params.fungibleTokenId: Inventory token id of the fungible tokens to bundle in a Lot item.

setInventoryContract(address).details: Sets the inventory contract to use in the delivery of purchased Lot items.

params.inventoryContract: Address of the inventory contract to use.

setPayoutTokenAddress(address).details: Sets which token to use as the payout currency from the Lot sales.

params.payoutTokenAddress: Payout currency token contract address to use.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateLotFungibleAmount(uint256,uint256).details: Updates the given Lot's fungible token amount bundled with each NFT.

params.fungibleAmount: Fungible token amount to update with.
params.lotId: Id of the Lot to update.

updateLotNonFungibleSupply(uint256,uint2.details: Updates the given Lot's non-fungible token supply with additional NFTs. There are NO guarantees about the uniqueness of the non-fungible token supply.

params.lotId: Id of the Lot to update.

updateLotPrice(uint256,uint256).details: Updates the given Lot's item sale price.

params.lotId: Id of the Lot to update.
params.price: The new sale price, in payout currency tokens, to update with.

updateNonFungibleSupply(uint256[],uint25.details: Sets or updates the nonFungibleSupply for the sale.
